<p>[:en]</p>
<h1 id="about-fairytale-legends-red-riding-hood">About Fairytale Legends: Red Riding Hood</h1>
<p>In Fairy Tale Legends: Red Riding Hood players are taken on a fantastical journey through the forest. During this journey you’re encountering magical fairies and of course the Big Bad Wolf. Having no less than seven bonus features this slot is never boring. This slot is running on a the standard five reels, three lines board with bet lines fixed at 20.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game features</h2>
<p>This slot is a truly shining example when it comes to features. Seven features is what’s making this game stand out. Sticking to the fairytale theme of the game there is a fairy magically transforming symbols in all of these features with the exception of the bonus features.</p>
<h3 id="sticky-wild-re-spins">Sticky Wild Re-Spins</h3>
<p>During regular play Wild symbols appear on reels 2-4 and on all reels during free spins. Activating Sticky Wild Re-Spins requires 2 or more Wild symbols. Other Wilds appearing on a re-spin triggers another re-spin. On these re-spins the Wild symbols will be remaining where they are. Activating random or bonus features during a re-spin is not possible. In rare cases where three bonus symbols and two or more wilds are appearing on the board simultaneously the Bonus Feature is played first.</p>
<h3 id="random-features">Random Features</h3>
<p>There are three Random Features in this slot. They are known as Fairy Magic Spin, Fairy Surprise and Fairy Wild Spin. All of them are randomly activated during regular game rounds and cannot get activated during Bonus Features, free spins or re-spins.</p>
<h4 id="fairy-magic-spin">Fairy Magic Spin</h4>
<p>This feature creates a cluster of five to nine medium win symbols on the reels for one spin only.</p>
<h4 id="fairy-surprise">Fairy Surprise</h4>
<p>Activating this Random Feature requires a no win spin. Once active the fairy chooses a symbol and starts transforming other symbols (starting with the lowest) into that symbol. The transformation of symbols stops once a win is awarded. Neither Bonus nor Wild symbols can be selected by the fairy.</p>
<h4 id="fairy-wild-spin">Fairy Wild Spin</h4>
<p>Three or four Wild symbols appears on reels 2 two to four. Since there are at least three Wilds on the board a re-spin is always activated. Just like in a normal spin further Wilds appearing activates additional re-spins.</p>
<h3 id="bonus-features">Bonus Features</h3>
<p>There is three bonus features in Fairytale Legends: Red Riding Hood. Activating them requires three bonus symbols appearing. Bonus symbols can only appear on reels one three and five. Once the bonus feature is active the player chooses one out of three identical chests. Choosing a chest activates either Beware the Wolf, Free Spins or Coin Win.</p>
<h4 id="beware-the-wolf-bonus-game">Beware the Wolf Bonus Game</h4>
<p>Activating the Beware the Wolf Bonus Game moves the Red Riding Hood to a board game like map. You move around by clicking the screen to activate a “die” roll (it looks nothing like a die but moves you a random number between one and six). In this game there are five different types of locations. They are the Coin Win, Arrow, Double, Jackpot Coin Win and finally Collect.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Coin Win</strong>: Multiplies your bet by the number on you’re landing on.</li>
<li><strong>Arrow</strong>: Changes the direction of your next move to that of the arrow.</li>
<li><strong>Double</strong>: Doubles your next win.</li>
<li><strong>Jackpot Coin Win</strong>: One of two ways of ending the game landing here wins you your bet multiplied by either one hundred or a massive two hunded with a Double.</li>
<li><strong>Collect</strong>: Finally we have collect, the second way of ending the game. The Big Bad Wolf jumps out, catching Red Riding Hood thus ending the Bonus Game.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h4>
<p>Activating Free Spins gives the player ten Free Spins using the same bet level and coin value as the activating round. While active  one bonus symbol rewards a player with 2 additional Free Spins, two Bonus symbols gives four more Free Spins with three giving the usual ten. During Free Spins Wilds can be appearing on all reels not just reel two to four. Other than that the game operates as normal.</p>
<h4 id="coin-win">Coin Win</h4>
<p>Activating the coin win feature awards the current bet multiplied by fifteen, immediately.</p>
<h2 id="game-details">Game Details</h2>
<ul>
<li>Developer: <a href="netent.com">NetEnt</a></li>
<li>Reels &amp; lines: 5 reels, 3rows &amp; 20 bet lines (fixed)</li>
<li>Bet levels: 1-10</li>
<li>Coin values (€): 0.01, 0.02, 0.05, 0.10, 0.20, 0.50, 1</li>
<li>Minimum bet: €0.2</li>
<li>Maximum bet: €200</li>
<li>Maximum win: €4,000 / 4,000 coins on a single bet line</li>
<li>Hit frequency: 19,90%</li>
<li>Bonus game: Yes</li>
<li>Jackpot: No</li>
</ul>
